title: Dakine Womens Heli Pro DLX Pack
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2013 Womens Heli Pro DLX Pack.
Womens Heli Pro DLX Features:
- Contoured harness designed specifically to fit a woman's frame
- Vertical snowboard carry
- Horizontal snowboard carry
- Retractable cable ski carry
- Snow tool/sho
